event CreateDao(address indexed dao, string name, string description, address creator, address referer)

event ImplementationUpgrade(uint256 indexed versionId, address daoImplementation, address membershipImplementation, address liquidPoolImplementation, address memberTokenImplementation, address governImplementation, address adamImplementation, address accountSystemImplementation, string description)
event OwnershipTransferred(address indexed previousOwner, address indexed newOwner)

function createDao(tuple(string _name, string _description, address baseCurrency, uint256 maxMemberLimit, string _memberTokenName, string _memberTokenSymbol, address[] depositTokens, address _referer, address[] _priceGateways) params, bytes[] data) returns (address)

function hashVersion(address _daoImplementation, address _membershipImplementation, address _liquidPoolImplementation, address _memberTokenImplementation, address _governImplementation, address _accountSystemImplementation) pure returns (uint256)

function initialize(address _daoImplementation, address _membershipImplementation, address _liquidPoolImplementation, address _memberTokenImplementation, address _accountSystemImplementation, address[] _budgetApprovalImplementations, address[] _priceGatewayImplementations, address _governFactory, address _team)

function upgradeImplementations(address _daoImplementation, address _membershipImplementation, address _liquidPoolImplementation, address _memberTokenImplementation, address _accountSystemImplementation, address _governImplementation, string description)
function upgradeToAndCall(address newImplementation, bytes data) payable
